<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="closing-a-document" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Closing a Document</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p>You can close the current document only or close Serna window with all opened documents.</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Close the current document only.</cmd>
        <info>To close the current document only, do one of the following:</info>
        <choices>
          <choice>Choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Close Document</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</choice>
          <choice>Press <uicontrol>Ctrl-W</uicontrol>.</choice>
          <choice>Click the <uicontrol>Close Document</uicontrol> button <image href="close-document-button.png" align="center"/> in the top right corner of the <xref href="menus.xml">main menu</xref>.</choice>
<?serna-redline-start 0 add screenshot?>          <choice>Right-click the <xref href="document-tabs.xml">document tab</xref> and select <uicontrol>Close Document</uicontrol> from the context menu.</choice>
<?serna-redline-end?>        </choices>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Close all opened documents.</cmd>
        <info>To close Serna window with all opened documents, do one of the following:</info>
        <choices>
          <choice>Choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Close Window</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</choice>
          <choice>Press <uicontrol>Alt-F4</uicontrol>.</choice>
          <choice>Click the <uicontrol>Close</uicontrol> button <image href="close-button.png" align="center"/> in the top right corner of Serna window.</choice>
        </choices>
      </step>
    </steps>
    <result>
      <p><note>
          <p>If you try to close a document that has been modified but not saved,  you will be asked what to do:</p>
          <image href="save-changes-dialog.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <p>To save the changes and close the document, click <uicontrol>Yes</uicontrol>.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>To close the document without saving the changes, click <uicontrol>No</uicontrol>.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>To cancel the closure of the document, click <uicontrol>Cancel</uicontrol>.</p>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </note></p>
    </result>
  </taskbody>
</task>
